OL,3,C'Mum won't survive': Families fear
OL,4,Cclosure of council-run care home
OL,6,FFamilies of elderly residents say they
OL,7,Fmay not survive if their care home
OL,8,Fcloses as part of a cash-strapped
OL,9,Fcouncil's cost cutting measures.
OL,11,FKnowle Manor Care Home in is at risk
OL,12,Funder 's proposals to save #63.9
OL,13,Fmillion in the next year.
OL,15,FAlmost 30 residents could be left
OL,16,Fhomeless.
OL,18,FCarol Allen's mother Barbara, who
OL,19,Fturns 90 this week, lives at the care
OL,20,Fhome.
