OL,3,C'Mum won't survive': Families fear
OL,4,Cclosure of council-run care home
OL,6,FCarol said: "I don't think my mum
OL,7,Fwould survive anywhere else. It's too
OL,8,Ftraumatic. Not just for my mum but it
OL,9,Fis traumatic, it's like being evicted
OL,10,Ffrom your home."
OL,12,FSharon Martin's mother, Margaret, 85,
OL,13,Fis another resident.
OL,15,FSharon said: "They are all very
OL,16,Fvulnerable people. A lot of them don't
OL,17,Fhave family and friends coming to
OL,18,Fvisit, so the people in the care home
OL,19,Fand the carers, they are their family."
