OL,3,C'Mum won't survive': Families fear
OL,4,Cclosure of council-run care home
OL,6,FCouncil leader James Lewis blamed the
OL,7,Fcouncil's predicament on "14 years of
OL,8,Fausterity".
OL,10,FHe said: "We are in a situation now
OL,11,Fwhere we have a further #60million
OL,12,Freduced from the council budget and
OL,13,Fthat means we have to make some very
OL,14,Fhard decisions including closing some
OL,15,Fmuch loved council facilities."
OL,17,FMore than 2,000 people have signed a
OL,18,Fpetition to save Knowle Manor.
