OL,6,FCllr Jane Senior said: "It's the last
OL,7,Fcouncil run home in Morley and we need
OL,8,Fit for our community and our residents.
OL,10,F"It's the impact it has on the
OL,11,Fresidents now, having to move at such
OL,12,Fan old age and they thought this was
OL,13,Fthere forever home."
OL,15,FA ouncil spokesperson said a
OL,16,Fconsultation was underway on the care
OL,17,Fhome's future.
