OL,7,Frecognise councils are facing
OL,8,Fchallenges and that is why we recently
OL,9,Fannounced an additional #600million
OL,10,Fsupport package for councils across
OL,11,FEngland, increasing their overall
OL,12,Ffunding for the upcoming financial
OL,13,Fyear to #64.7 billion ` a 7.5%
OL,14,Fincrease in cash terms.
OL,16,F"This additional funding has been
OL,17,Fwelcomed by leading local government
OL,18,Forganisations, but we remain ready to
OL,19,Ftalk to any concerned council about
OL,20,Fits financial position."
